{"tha-ap13:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap13:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap13:0.3":"Sihasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap13:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap13:1.2":"siddhatthe dvipaduttame; ","tha-ap13:1.3":"Vittharike pavacane, ","tha-ap13:1.4":"bahujannamhi sasane. ","tha-ap13:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap13:2.2":"sihasanamakasaham; ","tha-ap13:2.3":"Sihasanam karitvana, ","tha-ap13:2.4":"padapithamakasaham. ","tha-ap13:3.1":"Sihasane ca vassante, ","tha-ap13:3.2":"gharam tattha akasaham; ","tha-ap13:3.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap13:3.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap13:4.1":"Ayamena catubbisa- ","tha-ap13:4.2":"yojanam asi tavade; ","tha-ap13:4.3":"Vimanam sukatam mayham, ","tha-ap13:4.4":"vittharena catuddasa. ","tha-ap13:5.1":"Satam kannasahassani, ","tha-ap13:5.2":"parivarenti mam sada; ","tha-ap13:5.3":"Sonnamayanca pallankam, ","tha-ap13:5.4":"byamhe asi sunimmitam. ","tha-ap13:6.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap13:6.2":"dibbayanam upatthitam; ","tha-ap13:6.3":"Pasada sivika ceva, ","tha-ap13:6.4":"nibbattanti yadicchakam. ","tha-ap13:7.1":"Manimaya ca pallanka, ","tha-ap13:7.2":"anne saramaya bahu; ","tha-ap13:7.3":"Nibbattanti mamam sabbe, ","tha-ap13:7.4":"sihasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap13:8.1":"Sonnamaya rupimaya, ","tha-ap13:8.2":"phalikaveluriyamaya; ","tha-ap13:8.3":"Paduka abhiruhami, ","tha-ap13:8.4":"padapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap13:9.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap13:9.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap13:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap13:9.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap13:10.1":"Tesattatimhito kappe, ","tha-ap13:10.2":"indanama tayo jana; ","tha-ap13:10.3":"Dvesattatimhito kappe, ","tha-ap13:10.4":"tayo sumananamaka. ","tha-ap13:11.1":"Samasattatito kappe, ","tha-ap13:11.2":"tayo varunanamaka; ","tha-ap13:11.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap13:11.4":"catudipamhi issara. ","tha-ap13:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap13:12.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap13:12.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap13:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap13:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sihasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap13:14.1":"Sihasanadayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}